<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>658</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>dōu shì xíng lù rén 迦南658</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì xíng lù rén, wǒ yě shì xíng lù rén,
 dōu yào yǐ chéng xiāng shì. yī yàng piào liú de xīn,
 méi bì yào ràng rén dōu lǐ jiě wǒ men.
 yī gè xīn yuàn yào fú shì yòu zhēn yòu huó de shén.
 rú guǒ dà shān hū huàn, jiù zǒu xiàng dà shān.
 rú guǒ yuǎn fāng hū huàn, jiù zǒu xiàng yuǎn fāng.
 bèi qǐ xíng náng, fēng yǔ bù néng dǎng.
 dào suǒ duō mǎ de dà jiē xiǎo xiàng, bǎ jǐng zhōng qiāo xiàng.</lyrics>
</song>